<h1>Can you get Carer's Allowance?</h1>

<fieldset class="form-elements form-eligibility q1">
    <legend><span>Q2</span>Do you spend 35 hours or more each week caring for the person you care for?</legend>
    <p>For example, cooking meals, or helping them with their shopping.</p>
	<ul class="radio">
		<li><input type="radio" name="q2" id="yes"><label for="yes">Yes</label></li>
		<li><input type="radio" name="q2" id="no"><label for="no">No</label></li> 
	</ul>
    <div id="answerNoMessageWrap" class="prompt breaks-prompt eligibility-prompt" style="display: none;">
        <p>You can only qualify for Carer's Allowance if you are caring for this person , for 35 hours or more each week.</p>
        <p>You are legally entitled to claim Carer's Allowance even though you <strong>do not</strong> qualify and <strong>will not</strong> get Carer's Allowance.</p>
    </div>
</fieldset>
